                </div>
                <h3 class="competency-name">Critical Thinking</h3>
                <p class="competency-description">
                    The ability to analyze complex situations, identify root causes, and make 
                    informed decisions based on evidence and sound reasoning rather than assumptions.
                </p>
                <p class="competency-application">
                    <strong>Application:</strong> Evaluating market opportunities, assessing competitive landscapes, 
                    and making strategic pivots based on data and customer feedback.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="competency-card">
                <div class="competency-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="competency-name">Financial Literacy</h3>
                <p class="competency-description">
                    Understanding financial statements, managing cash flow, budgeting effectively, 
                    and making investment decisions that ensure long-term sustainability.
                </p>
                <p class="competency-application">
                    <strong>Application:</strong> Creating realistic financial projections, identifying funding needs, 
                    controlling costs, and allocating resources to maximize value creation.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="competency-card">
                <div class="competency-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="competency-name">Resilience & Adaptability</h3>
                <p class="competency-description">
