                    strategies in response to changing circumstances without losing sight of core values.
                </p>
                <p class="competency-application">
                    <strong>Application:</strong> Navigating market downturns, responding to competitive pressures, 
                    and recovering from operational challenges with renewed focus and energy.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="competency-card">
                <div class="competency-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="competency-name">Leadership & Collaboration</h3>
                <p class="competency-description">
                    Inspiring and guiding teams toward shared goals, building strong relationships, 
                    and creating environments where diverse talents can contribute and thrive.
                </p>
                <p class="competency-application">
                    <strong>Application:</strong> Building high-performing teams, fostering organizational culture, 
                    negotiating partnerships, and motivating stakeholders around a common vision.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="competency-card">
                <div class="competency-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="competency-name">Creative Innovation</h3>
                <p class="competency-description">
                    Generating novel solutions to problems, thinking beyond conventional approaches, 
                    and combining ideas in unexpected ways to create unique value propositions.
                </p>
                <p class="competency-application">
                    <strong>Application:</strong> Developing differentiated products, designing innovative service 
                    models, and creating compelling brand experiences that resonate with customers.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="competency-card">
                <div class="competency-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="competency-name">Ethical Decision-Making</h3>
                <p class="competency-description">
                    Consistently choosing actions aligned with moral principles, considering impacts 
                    on all stakeholders, and building businesses that operate with integrity.
                </p>
                <p class="competency-application">
                    <strong>Application:</strong> Establishing fair labor practices, ensuring transparent operations, 
                    prioritizing customer welfare, and making choices that balance profit with social good.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
