            <p class="vision-content">
                These three ventures represent more than separate business ideas—they form an 
                interconnected vision where each strengthens the others. The accounting firm provides 
                financial stability and scholarship opportunities. The restaurant creates demand for 
                the farm's produce while serving as a community gathering place. The farm supplies 
                fresh ingredients while demonstrating environmental responsibility. Together, they 
                model how entrepreneurship can create economic, social, and environmental value 
