    <section id="closing" class="closing">
        <div class="closing-content">
            <h2 class="closing-title">From Vision to Value</h2>
            <p class="closing-reflection">
                Entrepreneurship is not a destination but a continuous journey of learning, 
                adapting, and creating. It demands courage to begin, persistence to continue, 
                and humility to recognize that success is measured not just in financial returns 
                but in lives improved and communities strengthened.
            </p>
            <p class="closing-commitment">
                I commit to building businesses that operate with integrity, serve with purpose, 
                and contribute meaningfully to the world around them. This means prioritizing 
                long-term sustainability over short-term gains, valuing people as much as profits, 
                and recognizing that true wealth is created when everyone prospers together.
            </p>
            <div class="closing-credo">
                <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> 
                "Success is not measured by what we accumulate, but by what we contribute. 
                The greatest entrepreneurial legacy is not built on balance sheets alone, 
                but on the positive change we create in the lives of others."
            </div>
